Suppose that resistor values are chosen that do not precisely satisfy Eq. 5.23. Instead, the relationship among the resistors $R_{\mathrm{a}}, R_{\mathrm{b}}, R_{\mathrm{c}}$, and $R_{\mathrm{d}}$ is

